title: Kingdom of God is Within You ,  Leo Tolstoy - mp3 - Gandhi, King
description:
!!!!! Tolstoy says read INTRO and then LAST 2 CHAPTERS FIRST !!!!!!!!!

!!!PLEASE SEED. PLEASE SHARE!!!

This boy transformed Gandhi in England as a student and became the Bible of he and his followers in Sourth Africa and beyond.

Tolstoy through this writing was the father of Gandhi and possibly of Martin Luther King, both men having read him in their youth and been transformed to the giants of humanity we know them as.
